Executing Tests: 
ex:
State ID   Description        
 S1        User not logged in 
 S2        User logged in     
 S3        Item added to cart 
 S4        Order placed 

 Event ID  Input / Action   
 E1        Login            
 E2        Add item to cart 
 E3        Place order      
 E4        Logout           
   
   The user starts in S1 (Not Logged In).
   After login (E1), they go to S2 (Logged In).
   They can add an item (E2) â†’ moves to S3 (Item Added to Cart).
   When they place the order (E3), they reach S4 (Order Placed).
   Logout (E4) always takes them back to S1 (Not Logged In)
